About Us

About Green Turf Landscaping

Geelong's Natural Elegance Crafted by Green Turf Landscaping. Transforming Spaces, Elevating Dreams.

Green Turf Landscaping is known for its meticulously crafted outdoor spaces that show off the best that nature has to offer.

Founded in 2017 and has since grown into a top Landscaping Service in Geelong.

Today, our dedicated team brings passion, skill, and experience into all of the projects that we do. With a variety of services available, clients have many options when it comes to their vision for their outdoor space. We believe in creating spaces that are as beautiful as they are functional, always putting customer satisfaction first.
